cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SD 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with ASR (Automatic Speech Recognition) performance prediction using CNNs that encode both text and speech. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech signal embeddings and their analysis. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possible category as the paper deals with multi-task learning and tagging utterances according to their speech style, accent, and broadcast program origin. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper deals with deep learning models and their learned representations. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with speech signal embeddings and their analysis.
